589
00:32:52,027 --> 00:32:54,027
It was an accident.

590
00:32:54,029 --> 00:32:55,630
What are you doing here?

591
00:32:55,632 --> 00:32:58,098
Tyler Mitchell just got loaded
into an ambulance.

592
00:32:58,100 --> 00:33:00,301
