00:33:19,991 --> 00:33:23,659
- He had great manners.
- He told us to keep it a secret.

602
00:33:23,661 --> 00:33:25,761
A, I'm your sister.

603
00:33:25,763 --> 00:33:27,429
And B, as a general rule,

604
00:33:27,431 --> 00:33:29,999
