Sarah.

672
00:36:42,100 --> 00:36:43,532
Mom.

673
00:36:43,534 --> 00:36:45,366
I'm disappointed.

674
00:36:45,368 --> 00:36:47,103
- Come on. Mom.
- Mom, please.

675
00:36:47,105 --> 00:36:48,271
[DOOR SLAMS]

676
